	// Add your code here

	
	var request = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('Outbound to Twilio','case create');
	request.setStringParameterNoEscape('casenum',current.number);
	request.execute();
	
	var response = request.execute();
	var requestBody = request.getRequestBody();
	var responseBody = response.getBody();
	var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
	gs.log(response.getBody());
	
	responseJSON = responseBody.substring(10,responseBody.length-1);
	parsedJSON = JSON.parse(responseJSON);
	var targetCaseNumber = parsedJSON["number"];
	
	var logString = "Greetings. A new case " +targetCaseNumber+" has been created.";
	gs.log(logString, "SNOW REST Test");
	
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-10-04 22:03:33</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>546a75a91b5c88106933fc88cc4bcb5c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Outbound to Twilio</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="CICD Test Application" source="x_11413_cicd_test">268e9d5fdbb32300fcf417803996195e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="CICD Test Application">268e9d5fdbb32300fcf417803996195e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_546a75a91b5c88106933fc88cc4bcb5c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-10-04 22:07:36</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=546a75a91b5c88106933fc88cc4bcb5c"/></record_update>
